Summary: Seemingly water vapor, half circle reflective to rising sun.
divs: Sighting Detailsview from amtrak train - trying to capture the tangerine and purple hues of the sunrise in early pre=dawn. i've one other viewing in another town in the west coast-daylite and white half circle - seemingly missed when taking the picture...towards the expanse of the landscape in the distance, same left corner....gotta dig it up. calmness for me in all possible viewings all my life
